{"tid":1915667,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[Steam遊戲企劃]如果我們都可以成為李超人？","createTime":"2020-03-08T11:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T11:36:09.000Z","uid":268272,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dc285dfa447ea39891c55d0c0cb036a70449f266","tid":1915667,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T11:18:07.000Z","msg":"係咁嘅，我哋係炎魔工作室，係一間新開嘅小型本土遊戲studio。<br />\n其實咁多位近排聽過誠哥個名，有冇諗過佢係點樣成為超人呢？我哋其實想重現地產商嘅發跡史，所以就想整個Game去比大家體驗下佢哋嘅發跡史，甚至整返自己嘅地產發跡史。<br />\n<br />\n你哋會問：其實你哋個Game同SimCity有咩分別呢？<br />\n咁SimCity係冇地皮呢個限制，亦都唔會同正苦嘈交，而我哋隻game希望重現返香港起樓嘅過程，同埋金融戇鳩野。仲有simcity要裝摸落去先有新嘅building，而我哋會預先裝定其他style嘅建築物，任君選擇，但係大家亦可以裝mod落去。<br />\n<br />\n上圖為不同style的建築物，80年代至千禧年代風格亦有。<br />\n而呢個game會有三個mode：<br />\n創業、上帝同埋故事。<br />\n創業就係當然係好似李超人咁樣創業做首富，而上帝即係sandbox。<br />\n最後就係故事mode。故事mode就係將本身創業mode嘅玩法，再加強難度之餘，再將成個game變成一個視&middot;覺&middot;小&middot;說。<br />\n你冇睇錯我亦都冇打錯，我哋想個故事mode變成一個鬥志之前有令人感動嘅Visual Novel，而文手更加痴線到想請聲優配音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可惜製作成本同埋請聲優全部都係要錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以我哋要<br />\n集氣！<br />\n突破！<br />\n掙扎！<br />\n<br />\n而呢個就係kickstarter 嘅link，希望大家可以入錢支持我哋團隊。多謝咁多位連登巴打睇完呢篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/studio-molo/soaring-tales-of-skylines\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Fstudio-molo%2Fsoaring-tales-of-skylines&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw9AsgxU2M8QNPxyQAqp636I%3D&h=6f9ea57a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/studio-molo/soaring-tales-of-skylines</a>"},{"pid":"a46f97dc850f494c783e2fbd80e879a885e69b4a","tid":1915667,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T11:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QD0WaVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQD0WaVU.jpg&h=f58931bd&s={SIZE}\" /> sorry唔記得上傳圖片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外我好似開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af42e3e3a539a4aeb485208d431d413b2dcdef24","tid":1915667,"uid":2590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:26:00.000Z","msg":"不如整個題材係講買唔起私樓排唔到公屋<br />\n最後訓街比車撞死 咁樣好似易d代入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff9c738866a3e61c08f7b4cfb6bf307384a9c08","tid":1915667,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T15:29:03.000Z","msg":"望住d漂亮高樓大廈喊出黎 買唔到forever"},{"pid":"ea78dc94720d209b8a35bd74be2decf296e4a2a2","tid":1915667,"uid":160257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e9bad293a354901465c01dc69f12171eb1b84b","tid":1915667,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:27:56.000Z","msg":"唔係話打擊你，但同樣有咁既技術做啲關於香港既賽車/rpg會容易過你用時事政事做主題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7035421ff994da729900c6558573735a1d267f","tid":1915667,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5e9bad293a354901465c01dc69f12171eb1b84b","tid":1915667,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:27:56.000Z","msg":"唔係話打擊你，但同樣有咁既技術做啲關於香港既賽車/rpg會容易過你用時事政事做主題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:29:16.000Z","msg":"如果呢個市場都係充斥着呢啲遊戲<br />\n就冇一啲其他類型嘅遊戲<br />\n咁就係冇突破性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07f248eb2db2b706adcd54b239b9a2ef4adfbc4","tid":1915667,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a7035421ff994da729900c6558573735a1d267f","tid":1915667,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5e9bad293a354901465c01dc69f12171eb1b84b","tid":1915667,"uid":37757,"like":0,"